      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">13.103</ph> Use of standing price quotations.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Authorized individuals do not have to obtain individual quotations for each purchase. Standing price quotations may be used if-</p>
         <ol id="d731e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d758e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            The pricing information is current; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d758e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The Government obtains the benefit of maximum discounts before award.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
